            "title": "滙豐維持股市「最大」看漲立場,稱地緣政治擔憂被過度放大",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1NrXWzHdkbSkHY6lcDfMsQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA601S5_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 滙豐銀行自解放日以來維持對風險資產最看漲的立場,認為投資者不需要中東緊張局勢完全解決市場就能繼續復甦,只需要邊際改善即可。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">[[pro_nomination |</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"在InvestingPro上獲取深度分析師研究、升級預測和股票級別洞察\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:在InvestingPro上獲取深度分析師研究、升級預測和股票級別洞察;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/landing-page?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">在InvestingPro上獲取深度分析師研究、升級預測和股票級別洞察</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">]]</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行表示,其定位框架繼續發出數月來最強烈的股票買入信號,並反駁了隨著信貸利差和股價接近升級前水平,預計將出現的投資者自滿情緒的呼聲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行表示:「在我們看來,『不那麼糟糕』的消息流動就已經足夠好了。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e43fe7e3-f4a1-3009-b7e8-61e3a071fd88-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span>滙豐</span></span>指出,美國的高頻活動和勞動力市場數據表現良好,稅收退款較2025年水平高出近15%,為消費者提供了額外緩衝。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行目前的定位是最大程度增持股票,重點關注亞洲新興市場、日本和歐洲(尤其是歐洲銀行),同時雙倍增持新興市場本地利率和增持高收益信貸。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滙豐表示,除了地緣政治背景之外,市場更重要的驅動因素是全球盈利前景。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司認為,過去兩個季度對人工智能的悲觀情緒導致美國科技股估值溢價幾乎消失,這為在滙豐所描述的各類資產可能進一步V型反彈之後,輪動回美國股市和科技股創造了條件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行指出,美國例外主義的回歸將國債收益率推回4.3%以上是一個長期風險,並將其描述為可能對各類資產產生廣泛壓力的「危險區」的當前門檻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82-%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7-%E7%9C%8B%E6%BC%B2%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-%E7%A8%B1%E5%9C%B0%E7%B7%A3%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E8%A2%AB%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7-113249828.html",
